            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Licinio <lb n="2"/>Secundo <lb n="3"/>accenso <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>patron</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> suo <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Licin</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> Surae <lb n="6"/>primo <expan><abbr>secund</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>tertio <expan><abbr>consul</abbr><ex>atu</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>eius <expan><abbr>IIIIIIvir</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustali</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>uliae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>U</abbr><ex>rbis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>riumphalis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Tarracon</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>et <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>F</abbr><ex>aventiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>uliae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ugustae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>aternae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Barc</abbr><ex>inonis</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan><expan><abbr>al</abbr><ex cert="low">erii</ex></expan> Syrus Gratus <lb n="12"/><expan><abbr>IIIIIIvir</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustales</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>uliae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>U</abbr><ex>rbis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>riumphalis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>arraconis</ex></expan> <lb n="13"/>amico optimo
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nur handschriftlich überliefert. Die angegebenen Maße sind aus alten Maßangaben (&amp;quot;&amp;quot;alto quatro palmas 1/2, ancho 3&amp;quot;&amp;quot;) umgerechnet. Z. 11: statt G(?)al(erii?) auch C(?)al(purnii?) möglich.</p>
            </div>
